{"tid":2206251,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"寶雲道燈柱的降頭 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-09-17T11:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T11:11:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be41ae5981faa801a0ab23318f004061c2d62747","tid":2206251,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200917/GJ4SJSUO65DPTGRLGXKHJF3LT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200917%2FGJ4SJSUO65DPTGRLGXKHJF3LT4%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=43bba8ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200917%2FGJ4SJSUO65DPTGRLGXKHJF3LT4%2F&h=61cdd014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200917/GJ4SJSUO65DPTGRLGXKHJF3LT4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n寶雲道燈柱的降頭 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y8R2qsQDIR2fEehhjyd2CqA4PVg=/803x455/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7ZZD63YSGNG4NCHLWAOBVPQU2E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy8R2qsQDIR2fEehhjyd2CqA4PVg%3D%2F803x455%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7ZZD63YSGNG4NCHLWAOBVPQU2E.png&h=2028a8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉劉周末到寶雲道行山，拍下電燈柱貼滿割價急售的豪宅盤街招。同樣是山頂區業主極有銀用的葉劉，點解釋這個現象？當然，對葉劉這種物體冇期望，奔七的她，絕口不提国安法，猛話黑暴與疫症拖累，令人投資失利兼且對香港失去信心，叫政府以實際行動令市民對香港重拾希望。<br />\n<br />\n實際行動？鄭市長冇回應被夾硬送中的12個市民的基本權利，由李家超代言，未開口已知是廢噏。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。無可能唔覺支針幾咁拮肉。不過呢，東山台雙車位那個筍盤，隨時成為鄭司長公司名下的獵物。業主敗走離場，司長卻迎難而上，還清兩層豪宅的按揭。<br />\n<br />\n今天，銀主，金主，天主都唔掂，中共加按在香港人頭上那條国安法，與智慧燈柱利疊利，下一代都還唔清。曾經是掃把頭的葉劉，與口裏說愛國身體最誠實的商家，感受到國家的降頭，行屍走肉mode照啟動，物業就加快脫手止蝕。"}]}